    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315130/extras/0cd2a6bbf28a2624f8e172443f76d41e.poster.avif?t=1751160498\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315130/extras/0cd2a6bbf28a2624f8e172443f76d41e.webm?t=1751160498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315130/extras/0cd2a6bbf28a2624f8e172443f76d41e.mp4?t=1751160498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the boots of soldiers entrenched in one of history’s most intense conflicts. <i>In Country – Vietnam</i> is a co-op shooter that thrusts you and up to four friends directly into the thick of combat, where you’ll need to rely on your brothers in arms to survive and succeed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315130/extras/102b257d3c26688f0bf88d95c3c95fd8.poster.avif?t=1751160498\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315130/extras/102b257d3c26688f0bf88d95c3c95fd8.webm?t=1751160498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315130/extras/102b257d3c26688f0bf88d95c3c95fd8.mp4?t=1751160498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> In Country – Vietnam</i> was crafted out of a deep desire to experience authentic, boots-on-the-ground gameplay in a historical setting. With a focus on an engaging, chaotic gameplay loop, this game features intense strike packages like Napalm that light up the battlefield, ambushes in dense jungle foliage that create suspenseful encounters, and attention to detail that honors the conflict’s reality while ensuring a truly enjoyable gameplay experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315130/extras/3dfb388b4c31852885367115e190c273.poster.avif?t=1751160498\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315130/extras/3dfb388b4c31852885367115e190c273.webm?t=1751160498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315130/extras/3dfb388b4c31852885367115e190c273.mp4?t=1751160498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your soldier with various era appropriate outfits to best suit your mission’s needs. Whether you’re relaxing on the FOB or returning to base from a long patrol, your soldier is a representation of your experience and prowess on the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315130/extras/dd11a05af13f52e86306d288db597443.avif?t=1751160498\" width=600 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In Country – Vietnam</i> is a game created by gamers, for gamers. We are dedicated to developing this project alongside our community. Your feedback helps shape the future of the game. With regular updates, new missions, game modes, and future content planned beyond release, <i>In Country – Vietnam</i> will continue to evolve long after its initial launch. Join our Discord, share your thoughts, and become part of the community. Welcome to the fight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
